@IpForensicsReport_Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5258

### Register
POST {{IpForensicsReport_Api_HostAddress}}/api/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Vladimir",
  "lastName": "Janevski",
  "email": "vladimir@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### Login
POST {{IpForensicsReport_Api_HostAddress}}/api/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vladimir@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}